description.text:
If you are using this for a MetalMagma hot end or a J-Head MK-V, download and print the parts that start with &quot;Magma.&quot;  
If you are using this with a J-Head MK-IV, download and print the Magma_Hot_End_Cooler_Mount.STL, Magma_Hot_End_Cooler_Revised.STL, Fan_Shroud_Left.STL, and the Filament_Cooler.STL.  The Fan_Shroud_Left.STL and Filament_Cooler.STL accommodate the taller height of the J-Head MK-IV.  
Fans attach with #4 machine screws. Mounts attach to cooling ducts w/ #6 machine screws.
